com.company.demo.user

Class ZUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.demo.user.ZUser

  • public class ZUser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for creating user objects. This is a model class which have getters and setters for its fields This class uses Utility class methods for generating HID and ZID.
    See Also:
    Utility.H_IDgenerator(), Utility.ZIDgenerator()
